channel.title: NewBreed - Development
channel.description:
Im starting / started a new server, and new client.
Im looking for experianced coders. Also looking for site coders, and maybe beta testers.
I have started using an original winter love realise. And for the client a new deob 317.
I am aiming for a good server. Nothing like runescape, just a good laugh. But want it coded properly.
Things i am aiming for
- Cheat proof 100% - Runescape Specials 100% (Including Spec Bar) - Already have the frame with filling - Good saving and loading - Generaly Bug Free.
To become a coder (server / client / web) Please post in this thread.
Website - [url=http://newbreed.5gbfree.com]Site[/url] Fourms - [url=http://newbreed.5gbfree.com/forums]Forums[/url] Download Page - [url=http://newbreed.5gbfree.com/download]Download Page[/url]
(link to the download page is there for the 317 deob)
Even if you dont want to become part of the project please post to show some support, After this is finished it will be 100% Open Source Free Download For All!
